comments: Smith (IND) briefly brushes Mann's (OKC) chest with his right hand on the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs.
Smith (IND) briefly applies a forearm to Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) side before making slight contact to his off-arm on the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) briefly ties-up the ball in Brissett's (IND) hands before dislodging it, and marginal contact occurs on the drive.
Roby (OKC) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Stephenson (IND) makes foot-to-foot contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Jackson (IND) steps out-of-bounds prior to the start of his drive.
Hield (IND) commits a take foul on Mann (OKC).
Brissett (IND) momentarily grasps Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) left arm before the two engage and disengage with one another during the rebound.
Brissett (IND) and Wiggins (OKC) both attempt to retrieve the rebound, and Wiggins goes to the floor after incidental leg-to-leg contact with Brissett.
Bazley (OKC) ends his dribble and takes two legal steps.
Haliburton (IND) applies a forearm to Bazley's (OKC) side that affects his SQBR.
Smith (IND) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Stephenson (IND) slides his left foot that is pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Smith (IND) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Stephenson (IND) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brissett (IND) commits a take foul on Bazley (OKC).
